{"title":"接待","authors":["天马"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":11,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"接待"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年把筋斗栽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年又飞来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对这样的不速之客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该怎样接待？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先例在，无须改，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民空军巧安排，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向天空热情招手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的“客人”请下来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意外？不意外！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇怪？不奇怪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上来的，我们欢迎；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上来的，也不亏待！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天罗地网张开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁有兴趣谁就来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干净、全部、彻底消灭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看咱们的能耐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禀性难移，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江山易改，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美蒋反动派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——花冈岩的脑袋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰了一回壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没讨一回乖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前车翻了后车来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞蛾扑火自遭灾！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且休要自怨自艾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不要互相责怪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们下次如再光临，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们还是一样接待！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然你们来时不通知，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鬼鬼祟祟不正派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们长有千里眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一看便知强盗来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管是来自天上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管是来自海外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接待一律平等，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包使你们“愉快”！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}